<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login - Bobot</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .wrapper { display: flex; width: 820px; min-height: 480px; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; }
    .left-panel { flex: 1; background: #2c3e50; color: #fff; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 48px 40px; }
    .left-panel .logo { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e8f4f8; }
    .left-panel .logo span { color: #3498db; }
    .left-panel .tagline { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #bdc3c7; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 12px; }
    .left-panel .features { margin-top: 28px; list-style: none; }
    .left-panel .features li { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #95a5a6; padding: 5px 0; }
    .left-panel .features li::before { content: 'â†’ '; color: #3498db; }
    .right-panel { flex: 1; padding: 48px 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
    .right-panel h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .right-panel .sub { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #7f8c8d; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .alert { padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .alert-error { background: #fdecea; color: #c0392b; border-left: 3px solid #e74c3c; }
    .alert-success { background: #eafaf1; color: #1e8449; border-left: 3px solid #2ecc71; }
    .demo-box { background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #e9ecef; border-radius: 7px; padding: 12px 14px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #555; }
    .demo-box .demo-title { font-weight: 600; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 7px; }
    .demo-box .demo-row { margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .demo-box .demo-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 10px; margin-right: 6px; color: #fff; }
    .badge-merchant { background: #f39c12; }
    .badge-user { background: #3498db; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: 500; }
    .form-group input { width: 100%; padding: 10px 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2c3e50; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
    .form-group input:focus { border-color: #3498db; }
    .btn-submit { width: 100%; padding: 11px; background: #2c3e50; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 6px; transition: background 0.2s; }
    .btn-submit:hover { background: #34495e; }
    .link-row { text-align: center; margin-top: 18px; font-size: 0.83rem; color: #7f8c8d; }
    .link-row a { color: #3498db; text-decoration: none; }
    .link-row a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="left-panel">
      <div class="logo">Bo<span>bot</span></div>
      <p class="tagline">Platform manajemen transaksi dan merchant untuk bisnis Anda.</p>
      <ul class="features">
        <li>Kelola merchant dengan mudah</li>
        <li>Pantau transaksi secara real-time</li>
        <li>Laporan keuangan terstruktur</li>
        <li>Akses kapan saja &amp; di mana saja</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="right-panel">
      <h2>Masuk ke Akun</h2>
      <p class="sub">Selamat datang kembali!</p>

      <div class="demo-box">
        <div class="demo-title">ðŸ”‘ Demo Kredensial</div>
        <div class="demo-row">
          <span class="badge badge-merchant">Merchant</span>
          Email: <strong>admin@example.com</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Password: <strong>123456</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-row">
          <span class="badge badge-user">User</span>
          Email: <strong>user@example.com</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Password: <strong>123456</strong>
        </div>
      </div>

      <% if (error) { %><div class="alert alert-error"><%= error %></div><% } %>
      <% if (success) { %><div class="alert alert-success"><%= success %></div><% } %>

      <form action="/login" method="post">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Email</label>
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="contoh@email.com" >
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Password</label>
          <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Masukkan password" >
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Masuk</button>
      </form>
      <div class="link-row">Belum punya akun? <a href="/register">Daftar sekarang</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
